briefdescription.para: Class representing a P1 field on a VEF mesh.

detaileddescription.para: This class inherits from Champ_Inc_P1_base and manages a nodal (P1) field defined on a VEF (Finite Element Volumes) discretized domain.

It provides:
Access to the associated Domaine_VEF
A method to print the field values at mesh vertices
